name: Fatigue
description: A feeling of extreme tiredness or lack of energy, often making it difficult to carry out daily tasks.

name: Breathlessness
description: A feeling of shortness of breath or difficulty breathing, which can be caused by various health conditions.

name: Dizziness
description: A sensation of lightheadedness, unsteadiness, or a feeling that you or your surroundings are spinning.

name: Chest Pain
description: A discomfort or pain in the chest area, which can vary from a sharp or stabbing sensation to a pressure-like feeling.
